<plot>Broadcast daily over the "spring break" in 1971 as a pilot, the show was hosted by Dinah Shore and co-hosted by various other game show hosts of the day. (Alex Trebek, etc.) Children had to guess famous events or persons as mimes acted out scenes accompanied by Corky Greene who created live music and vocal sound effects accompaniment.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?242726</url></doc>
